Faculty curator Noah Whiteman was just named a Guggenheim Fellow. Noah works on a diverse set of topics involving plant-animal coevolution. Please see the news story here: <a href="https://www.gf.org/fellows/all-fellows/Noah-Whiteman/"> https://www.gf.org/fellows/all-fellows/Noah-Whiteman/</a> and Noah’s Lab website here: <a href="http://www.noahwhiteman.org/">http://www.noahwhiteman.org/</a>
