<td>
<!-- 2016-05-23 -->
<!-- May 23, 2016 -->
<p align="center"><blockquote class="pageMajorHeading">
<span class="copyrightText">May 23, 2016</span><br>
SO BE FREE 22 to be held March 27 - 30, 2017, in the lower elevations of the Sierra Nevada, near Sequoia National Park. Participants will see a variety of spectacular habitats that are very rich in bryophytes, including the foothills where the valley fog hits the rock outcrops and oak savannahs. The geology includes marble as well as granitics. Depending on snowpack, we may be able to go to the giant sequoia forests. <b>Registration Deadline is Dec. 15, 2016.</b>
<a href="http://bryophyte.cnps.org/images/pdf/SBF22.pdf">Registration details here.</a></blockquote>
