<td align="center" valign="top" class="bodyText"><p align="left"><span class="pageMajorHeading"><a name="VOL" id="VOL">Curatorial Volunteers Needed at University and Jepson Herbaria.</a></span><br /></p>
<p align="left">
<img src="/common/images/activities/VolunteerSat.jpg" alt="" width="280" height="161" hspace="5" align="left" />
One Saturday of each month is a Volunteer Day in the Herbaria. Work with Herbaria staff to help prepare mounted plant specimens and database collections. <span class="horizMenuLinks"><a href="/main/volunteer.html">Learn more about how you can help!</a></span><br /></p>
<p align="left"><strong>Dates for 2019-2020: September 7,&nbsp;&nbsp;October 5,&nbsp;&nbsp;November 2,&nbsp;&nbsp;December 7,&nbsp;&nbsp;February 8,<br />March 7,&nbsp;&nbsp;April 18 (Cal Day),&nbsp;&nbsp;May 9.</strong><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /></p>
